@inherits AdminComponentBase

<Overview3Cols>
    <Text1>
        <strong>Diagnostic</strong> is a comprehensive tool that performs automated health checks and analysis of Proxmox VE environments.<br />
        It scans clusters, nodes, and virtual machines to identify configuration issues, performance problems, and potential system failures.<br />
        The module schedules regular diagnostic scans to proactively detect issues before they impact system operations.<br />
    </Text1>

    <Text2>
        <strong>Scheduled Health Checks</strong>: Automates regular diagnostic scans using configurable cron schedules.<br />
        <strong>Proactive Issue Detection</strong>: Identifies misconfigurations, hardware problems, and performance bottlenecks early.<br />
        <strong>Comprehensive Analysis</strong>: Examines system logs, configurations, and resource utilization patterns.<br />
        <strong>Issue Tracking</strong>: Maintains history of discovered problems and allows ignoring known non-critical issues.<br />
    </Text2>

    <Text3>
        <strong>Seamless Integration</strong>: Works natively with Proxmox VE API to collect comprehensive system information.<br />
        <strong>Actionable Results</strong>: Provides clear descriptions of issues with recommendations for resolution.<br />
        <strong>Maintenance Efficiency</strong>: Reduces manual system monitoring and enables predictive maintenance strategies.<br />
    </Text3>
</Overview3Cols>
